tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE user_interactions ( user_id INT, interaction_date TIMESTAMP, chatbot_id INT, message VARCHAR(255), response_time INT );

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    chatbot_id INT,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_message TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE chatbot_stats (
    stat_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    chatbot_id INT,
    total_interactions INT,
    average_response_time INT,
    most_common_user_interaction TEXT,
    last_interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE chatbot_sessions (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    start_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    end_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    chatbot_id UUID,
    user_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE User_Interactions (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    chatbot_id UUID,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ,
    interaction_type TEXT,
    message TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE chatbot_conversations (
    convo_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    conversation_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE chatbot_messages (
    message_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    convo_id INT,
    sender VARCHAR(50),
    message_text TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE chatbot_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    convo_id INT,
    rating INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
